('276', 'Jefferson Davis Electric Cooperative', '', '906 N. Lake Arthur Avenue Jennings LA 70546', 'http://www.jdec.org/', 'P.O. Drawer 1229 Jennings LA 70546', 'jdelectric41@yahoo.com', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'b)         Election and Tenure: In the year 1979 nine board consumer/members shall be elected                 to office. Each board consumer/member shall represent  one of the nine districts and                 shall be elected in conformance with procedures as hereinafter described                 except that the term of office for each will be as follows: The board                 consumer/members representing District 1 4 and 7 shall each be elected to serve until                 the annual meeting to be  held in the year 1980 or until their successors                 shall have been elected and shall have qualified.  The board consumer/members                 representing District 2 5 and 8 shall each be elected to serve until the                 annual meeting to be held in the year 1981 or until  heir successors shall                 have been elected and shall have qualified.   The board consumer/members                         representing Districts 3 6 and 9 shall each be elected to serve until the                 annual meeting to be held in the year 1982 or until their successors shall                 have been elected and shall have qualified. Beginning in the year 1980                 three board consumer/members shall each be elected for a three year term to fill the                 vacancies caused by expiration of the incumbent terms of office. ', '', '', '22'),
